{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic| name=Mobiliarbus| type=[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic#Spells|Spell]] (Charm)| features=Causes movement of a tree| appearance=[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Books/Prisoner of Azkaban|''Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban'']]}}
== Overview ==
'''''Mobiliarbus''''', a rather specialized charm, is used to move a tree.
== Extended Description ==
{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Beginner Spoiler}}
[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Characters/Hermione Granger|Hermione]] uses this spell to move a Christmas tree in The Three Broomsticks, to better hide [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Characters/Harry Potter|Harry]] from a number of teachers who have just walked in.
