|rationale   = In order to illustrate how to use this specific software to create Trainz content step by step screen shots of the product in use help clarify to the reader exactly what they should be doing.  It can be quite difficult to describe a graphical user interface with multiple drop down menus in words so that the reader can follow quite complex procedures.
}}

