[[Image:Crochet-round.jpg|right|thumb|250px|Crocheting a round]] '''Working in rounds''' in crochet does not require any special equipment. Unlike knitting, where special needles may be necessary, an ordinary crochet hook can work in rounds.
== Getting started == Make a chain of four stitches. Then stitch into the start of the chain to make a loop.
